The Andromeda 0.2.1 release contains bug fixes and new features.

The most important changes are listed in this document. For a complete
list of changes, see the Git log for the Andromeda sources that
you can check out from the public Git repository. For example:

git clone git@github.com:ABBAPOH/Andromeda.git
git log --cherry-pick --pretty=oneline v0.2..v0.2.1

Global
   * Fix Windows menu to switch between dialogs too
   * Fix Windows menu to disable switching when there's only one window
   * Fix opening urls from command line
   * Fix history
   * Add popup menu in back/forward buttons in tool bar
   * Fix compilation problems with gcc 4.7
   * Fix updating actions when changing active window

